:1477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<br />\n佢地班口撐支那唔緊要<br />\n肉體懼怕支那先最實際<br />\n正如有d 人口裡反美心，身體卻去食元氣<br />\n呢d 真係唔太實際囉<br />\n<br />\n為左節流<br />\n大家快d share 文宣比長者睇<br />\n支那嘅恐怖真係隨時影響到香港<br />\n到時棺材都無埋就好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3ADQhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3ADQhD.jpg&h=fbfa3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L003CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L003CF.jpg&h=0bf8c277&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51fd4b51d31e8d55bb7338582ee0f97d9459690a","tid":1682651,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"中共係咁架啦...無問題呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23b814157bfa2881ca004f1c7df7d163824d482","tid":1682651,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"我呢一生有望見證支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b7265c316cd827c8fb275dafdbf38d756a0b1ee","tid":1682651,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:34:30.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜 <br />\n講咗 中共賜你發財 就賜你入獄"},{"pid":"1d4bc4dc8364360791ffb217b14c26236e7187c2","tid":1682651,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1fcd5a1b0c1fe195e03f5251bbd6d42e82d46cf3","tid":1682651,"uid":197121,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T07:40:35.000Z","msg":"中共： 養肥左夠鐘剖黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"中囯人唔會發覺嘅<br />\n<br />\n中囯人都係愚民樂"},{"pid":"411aec582bdcb5860d9b7e93d244e71a74bca634","tid":1682651,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"